What you need to know:  They can take the matches to Kakamega, Bungoma or even Lodwar but we can assure them that we will always follow them to the ends of the earth to offer them their usual dose of beating.Now to the sad news and I was least amused when after the Madaraka Day clash, some AFC Leopards supporters, exposing the little they have between the ears, went to town castigating their goalkeeper Levis Opiyo solely on the basis of his ethnicity.